						<summary>

						<p>Stone pillar in the Varadarājasvāmi temple. (second side).</p>						

						<p>1132 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1055, Uttarāyaṇa sankrānti,</hi> which may correspond to 1132 A.D.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged. Seems to be a gift to the temple.</p>						

